how can i add ad credit

To add ad credit, you can follow these steps:
1. Log in to your News Break account.
2. Go to the 'Ad Management' section.
3. Select 'Add Credit' or a similar option.
4. Enter the amount you wish to add and your payment details.
5. Confirm the transaction.
